docs {
  Subscribe to receive notification anytime a new root is set by the validator.
  
  **Args**: None required
  
  **Returns**: Subscription ID that can be used to unsubscribe.
  
  **Notifications**: Returns the root slot number when a new root is set.
  
  **Note**: The root is the slot that has been finalized by the cluster.
}

